gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 133, Raptors 85
gameRecap.excerpt: Minnesota defeated Toronto, 133-85. Anthony Edwards led Minnesota with 28 points and six assists as Naz Reid added 23 points, six 3PM, and seven rebounds. Gradey Dick led Toronto with 16 points and eight rebounds in the loss. The Wolves improve to 53-23 as the Raptors fall to 23-53.
